{"tid":1378572,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好信林鄭下台嘅消息","createTime":"2019-07-28T16:10:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T16:36:02.000Z","uid":4564,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3d6771dc907d88ce4317bd54af932926197c9f2b","tid":1378572,"uid":4564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:10:21.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>28號（星期日）先去完689果個青少年軍夏令營結業禮，點會聽日就話因病下台<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n林鄭出席青少年軍事夏令營結業禮　籲放遠目光留心國家發展 (15:21)<br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥今日（28日）出席2019香港青少年軍事夏令營結業典禮，出席者還包括全國政協副主席董建華、中聯辦主任王志民、解放軍駐港部隊司令員陳道祥等。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥致辭時表示，在「一國兩制」的獨特優勢下，香港正受惠於國家高速發展所帶來的種種機遇，寄語同學要將目光放遠，多留心國家各方面發展，並以開放態度接觸不同的人和事，積極為自己人生增值，未來為香港、國家和世界的發展，各盡所能，作出貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥又稱，青年人是香港發展的動力，特區政府會盡力支持青年的健康成長，又呼籲同學能將夏令營中的體會和學習成果帶回學校，與同學分享，讓未來有更多同學參與此一有意義活動。"},{"pid":"59a506e6fba38483b758cb3a7a824955ff3c31ed","tid":1378572,"uid":4564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:11:28.000Z","msg":"PUSH<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3514ec2236a111c9555c83b4c8ba2fc5950fccc","tid":1378572,"uid":4564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:12:49.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"53441cb449e48eae1e3c64454161ef20c34a763c","tid":1378572,"uid":4564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-28T16:14:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"399647a7d59b625b26ff7cead4db61ae7b419207","tid":1378572,"uid":1747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":